# Go Click Exprice Backend - Project Plan

## Dependencies
- github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5 v5.2.0 - JWT (JSON Web Token) implementation
- github.com/gin-gonic/gin v1.9.1 - Web framework for building REST APIs
- gorm.io/driver/postgres v1.6.0 - PostgreSQL driver for GORM

## Project Overview
- **Admin Account**: Single admin account for management
- **Database**: PostgreSQL (internal database)
- **Email System**: SMTP for customer contact functionality
- **Server**: DigitalOcean droplet (1 GB Memory / 25 GB Disk / FRA1 - Ubuntu 25.04 x64)

## API Endpoints

### Blog Management
```
GET    /api/blogs              # Get all blog posts
GET    /api/blogs/:id          # Get single blog post
POST   /api/blogs              # Create new blog post
PUT    /api/blogs/:id          # Update blog post
DELETE /api/blogs/:id          # Delete blog post
GET    /api/blogs/public       # Get published blog posts (public)
```

### Contact Management
```
GET    /api/contacts           # Get all contact submissions (admin)
GET    /api/contacts/:id       # Get single submission (admin)
POST   /api/contacts           # Submit contact form (public)
PUT    /api/contacts/:id       # Update submission status (admin)
DELETE /api/contacts/:id       # Delete submission (admin)
```

## Additional Features
- **Image Handling**: Store image files with names only
- **Email System**: Users can send emails to admin via SMTP